Pre-Game Insights: USA Cricket announced its 15-member team for the forthcoming T20I bilateral series against Nepal, named the Stake Stars & Summit Trophy.
The Stake Stars and Summit Trophy is set to kick off on October 17th, 2024 at Grand Prairie Cricket Stadium in Grand Prairie, Texas, featuring three T20Is between Team USA and Nepal.

USA T20I Team includes Monank Patel (Captain), Andries Gous, Abhishek Paradkar, Aaron Jones, Harmeet Singh, Juanoy Drysdale, Muhammad Ali Khan, Milind Kumar, Nosthusha Kenjige, Jasdeep Singh, Saurabh Netravalkar, Saiteja Mukkamalla, Shayan Jahangir, Utkarsh Srivastava, Yasir Mohammad.
